{"tid":1327742,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"d hr打黎問current salary做咩？","createTime":"2019-07-17T17:05:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T05:06:04.000Z","uid":129169,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"da4eeebf7ca90a980382d3441e8dde02d3a71b1a","tid":1327742,"uid":129169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T17:05:03.000Z","msg":"今日收到個電話，就係hr打黎問我依家份工做緊咩，問我expected salary, 都ok, 但講完之後，佢又再問我，依份工係畢業第一份呀可？ <br />\n<br />\n之後問我current幾多，答完就睇下果個department會唔會叫我in<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 雖然我current計埋double pay除12姐，但個expected都係多20% 好似做左傻仔咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後都想問，current人工計埋double pay除12 係咪正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e852053ff9cd7002d1228acda8f9a06316a6236d","tid":1327742,"uid":10162,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T17:13:13.000Z","msg":"方便壓價囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a6b636e44bf27fe4d6e4ac1c2a73c981d8f92f9","tid":1327742,"uid":132047,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T17:14:36.000Z","msg":"通常 current salary 指係目前月薪(包埋自己果份MPF)，因為糧單有寫到時見工佢亦有可能要你攞埋比佢 check所以唔應該計埋 double paid。"},{"pid":"a8d5f66b8262d76b4b3b0e9a50769bca3cf9a2b8","tid":1327742,"uid":218504,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T17:17:05.000Z","msg":"我以前冇乜工作經驗加上之前嘅工作環境麻麻哋，心急想轉工。HR 問你攞current salary，加20%畀offer你。之前有個HR consultancy 係咁講。<br />\n<br />\n唔使理除乜，睇annual package, 覺得ok就去。唔等住轉或者你好掂嘅，就counter offer。不過你問得喱個問題，你應該都好fresh"},{"pid":"f3e7205f67e94ac217b5151587ba6a27e155f339","tid":1327742,"uid":129169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a8d5f66b8262d76b4b3b0e9a50769bca3cf9a2b8","tid":1327742,"uid":218504,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T17:17:05.000Z","msg":"我以前冇乜工作經驗加上之前嘅工作環境麻麻哋，心急想轉工。HR 問你攞current salary，加20%畀offer你。之前有個HR consultancy 係咁講。<br />\n<br />\n唔使理除乜，睇annual package, 覺得ok就去。唔等住轉或者你好掂嘅，就counter offer。不過你問得喱個問題，你應該都好fresh"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T17:25:00.000Z","msg":"上年先grad<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53cddcb9dcd67adfbb09da353507cd284a2a7886","tid":1327742,"uid":281598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T17:35:01.000Z","msg":"你應該答月薪幾多，如果double pay唔guarantee有，係要分開講。<br />\n<br />\n但你咁答都無所謂，如果年薪加福利同前景差過而家，你都唔會考慮㗎啦。"},{"pid":"24d8e9a623adcd54713491eb98030cb3804aa288","tid":1327742,"uid":218504,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f3e7205f67e94ac217b5151587ba6a27e155f339","tid":1327742,"uid":129169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a8d5f66b8262d76b4b3b0e9a50769bca3cf9a2b8","tid":1327742,"uid":218504,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T17:17:05.000Z","msg":"我以前冇乜工作經驗加上之前嘅工作環境麻麻哋，心急想轉工。HR 問你攞current salary，加20%畀offer你。之前有個HR consultancy 係咁講。<br />\n<br />\n唔使理除乜，睇annual package, 覺得ok就去。唔等住轉或者你好掂嘅，就counter offer。不過你問得喱個問題，你應該都好fresh"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T17:25:00.000Z","msg":"上年先grad<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T17:38:51.000Z","msg":"公司請人，你見工，大家對等。比較下而家份工同新工，滿意嘅就轉，唔啱就算。"},{"pid":"1885eebea73850da4b301a869a6bece1f867f3e7","tid":1327742,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T17:41:10.000Z","msg":"我會直接答annual package <br />\nbonus/commission有再分開講<br />\n<br />\n有公司12/13/14個月都有<br />\n直接講annual package expect+幾多%唔洗煩"},{"pid":"9bcbecebe5546aa61e5346a0a72ec0e70a09aff7","tid":1327742,"uid":28831,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T17:42:28.000Z","msg":"直接講年薪咪得<br />\n我做過一份工穩定出14個月<br />\n轉工個陣得12個月唔通蝕比佢？"},{"pid":"04aa1bd603e9c7f39a065830cbdfef9f4af72230","tid":1327742,"uid":196712,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T17:43:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"240d5390f5897a34